    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Internet-based discussion forums in which messages are exchanged via electronic mail, rather than through a bulletin board system or newsgroup. LISTSERV (TM) is a trademarked term for a commercial software product devoted to managing electronic mailing lists. Though "listserv" is often generically used to refer to any such software application, and commonly to mailing lists themselves, "electronic mailing lists" is preferred.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Discussieforums op internet waarin berichten worden uitgewisseld via elektronische post, en niet via een bulletinboard of nieuwsgroep. LISTSERV (TM), een gedeponeerd handelsmerk, is de naam van een commercieel softwareproduct dat specifiek is bedoeld voor het beheer van elektronische mailinglijsten. Hoewel 'listserv' meestal in algemene zin verwijst naar elke softwareapplicatie van dit type, en vaak ook naar mailinglijsten zelf, verdient de term 'elektronische mailinglijsten' de voorkeur.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>藉由電子郵件而非佈告欄系統或網路新聞群組、來交換訊息的網際網路論壇。LISTSERV (商標名)之名稱，指的是一個經過註冊的商業軟體產品，專門用來管理電子郵件清單。雖然「LISTSERV」一般常被用來指稱任一此類的應用軟體與郵件清單，但「電子郵件清單」一詞較為人所偏好。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Internetbasiertes Diskussionsforum, in dem Nachrichten per E-Mail ausgetauscht werden anstatt durch eine Mailbox oder eine Newsgroup. LISTSERV (TM) ist ein geschützter Begriff für eine kommerzielle Software zur Verwaltung von Mailinglisten. Obwohl "Listserv" allgemein verwendet wird, um auf jedes solcher Anwendungsprogramme zu verweisen und üblicherweise auch auf Mailinglisten selbst, wird "Mailingliste" bevorzugt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
